477
00:26:37,990 --> 00:26:39,450
Greetings, My Lord.

478
00:26:39,230 --> 00:26:43,770
[Mourn]

479
00:26:41,520 --> 00:26:42,760
You always

480
00:26:42,760 --> 00:26:43,990
put the memorial tablets

