00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:24,560
Mr. Qi,

498
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:25,690
My condolences.

499
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:27,840
We're here

500
00:27:27,840 --> 00:27:29,160
